ex=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Server selection</span><hr size=1> Bristlebane is among the highest server populations ;P, 3 guilds that can do AoW and NToV, with a couple others that shall be doing NToV. But we are still not a bad server if you can deal with the population.  <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=98739"><img src="http://stratosd.homestead.com/files/Sanaden.jpg"></a></center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usanadenrov.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sanaden RoV</A> at: 5/31/02 4:38:41 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utakatak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TAKATAK</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://homepage.ntlworld.com/elendil/teccie.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 48<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 5:57:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15328.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://homepage.ntlworld.com/elendil/holyknight.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Server selection</span><hr size=1> Dont choose Tholuxe Paells if you ask me, not a good atmosphere on that server. Most fun Ive had of late is DEFINITLEY Sullon Zek <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  good team way outranked atm and its SUCH fun to be the underdogs <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubizomb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bizomb</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fatcat </span><br>  Posts: 1186<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 6:31:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15328.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Server selection</span><hr size=1> Veeshan is ultra competitive server. We've also got several AoW enabled guilds as well as a large overseas population. So it's crowded 24/7. hehe. That being said, I don't think you are going to find many servers that don't have issues. <br>
<br>
Biz. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utienit1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tienit1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_yellowspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 26<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 6:59:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15328.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Server selection</span><hr size=1> /recommend Cazic-Thule<br>
